        "promptType": "=define",
        "text": "=You are a senior financial risk analyst.\n\nHere is the loan portfolio data:\n\nTotal Loans: {{$json.total_loans}}\nDefault Rate: {{$json.bad_loan_pct}}%\nHigh Risk Percentage with grade (D,E,F): {{$json.high_risk_pct}}%\n\nRegion-wise Default Rates:\n{{ JSON.stringify($json.region_risk) }}\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n- Determine overall risk level:\n  - If default rate > 12% → High\n  - If 8–12% → Medium\n  - Else → Low\n- Identify the most risky region using ONLY the given data\n- Sort regions by default_pct in descending order\n- Pick the highest as most risky\n- Show top 5 regions with their default percentages\n- Explain risk using only:\n  - Default rate\n  - High risk percentage\n  - Region concentration\n- DO NOT mention trends like increase/decrease\n- DO NOT invent any values or regions\n\nSTRICT RULES:\n- Use ONLY the provided data\n- Do NOT hallucinate\n- Output ONLY valid HTML (no markdown, no extra text)\n\nFORMAT:\n\n<h2 style=\"color:#2c3e50;\">📊 Weekly Loan Risk Summary</h2>\n\n<p><strong>Overall Risk Level:</strong> <span style=\"color:red;\">...</span></p>\n\n<h3>Key Metrics</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Total Loans:</strong> {{$json.total_loans}}</li>\n<li><strong>Default Rate:</strong> {{$json.bad_loan_pct}}%</li>\n<li><strong>High Risk Percentage:</strong> {{$json.high_risk_pct}}%</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>Most Risky Region</h3>\n<p>...</p>\n\n<h3>Key Insight</h3>\n<p>...</p>\n\n<h3>Regional Default Rates</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Region - Default %</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p style=\"font-size:12px;color:gray;\">\nThis is an automated risk report generated via n8n + GenAI pipeline.\n</p>",
